Title: Annual Conference — Keynote (CueScript Example)
Credit: Example file for CueScript v0.9
Author: CueScript
Format: CueScript v0.9 / Fountain

---

# ANNUAL CONFERENCE — MAIN STAGE

## Keynote Introduction

House lights at 80%. Music playing. Audience settles.

AUDIO (cue 1) [warn=30s]: Music fade standby

Presenter signals from side stage.

AUDIO (cue 1) [fade=4s, source=playback]: House music fade out
VIDEO (cue 1) [source=cam1, transition=cut]: Camera 1 — wide stage
LX (cue 1) [fade=3s]: Stage lights up — full

GRAPHICS (cue 1) [template=title_card, duration=10s]: Display conference title

Title holds. Applause builds.

GRAPHICS (cue 2) [template=lower_third, duration=8s]: Display "KEYNOTE SPEAKER — DR. ANNA REED"

SPEAKER enters from stage left.

AUDIO (cue 2) [source=lav_mic, gate=-20dB]: Activate speaker microphone
VIDEO (cue 2) [source=cam2, transition=cut, preset=single_shot]: Camera 2 — speaker medium

Applause fades.

SPEAKER
Thank you all for coming today.

GRAPHICS (cue 3) [template=presentation, source=laptop]: Display slide 1
VIDEO (cue 3) [source=screen, transition=cut]: Cut to presentation screen

Speaker gestures to screen.

CAMERA (cue 4) [preset=wide, speed=slow]: Pull back — wide shot of stage and screen
